Kovu 01
Kovu 01 is a [[zoophile]] with mental instability issues and an overdose of [[AIDS]]. He frequents [[FanFiction.Net]] and writes [[bullshit|stories]] for the [[Lion King]] fandom. His forums are renowned for being lulzbomb factories, in the same way that he is renowned for being the biggest lulzbomb of all time. 

{{quote2|U Fuck With Me Fucktard...And I Fuck With U, Got It!|Kovu 01|Internet brute}}

==A Brief History of Failure==

While Kovu's identification as a lolcow took place on the 13th of May, 2007, it is quite likely that he was trolled before then. However, his annoying tendency to [[delete fucking everything]] has rendered any chance of gathering historical lulz nearly zero. His official trolling began with reverse-text spam reviews that flooded his review boards. [[Image:UvoK1.jpg|thumb|!drater ,u2iaH]]

Worse was to follow. Just a few days later, Kovu realized he was being stalked by a "[[Cyrillic Millions Sign|backwards]]" person. [[Image:Eliforp.jpg|thumb|The profile in question.]] His [[Sock puppet|friends]] realized the impending disaster and quickly warned him of the obvious. Before long, his forum was flooded with the typical conspiracy theories that characterize the creative process of [[retards]]. [[Image:K01onoez.jpg|thumb|The beginning of epic lulz.]][[Image:Lolfightfightfight.jpg|thumb|Epic lulz.]]

